ebf k\u00fd l\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg/lo-dien-diem-moi-cua-dt-viet-nam-trong-nam-2018-292-183425.html\" target=\"_blank\">VFF v\u1edbi Acecook</span>, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"quang hai\" title=\"quang h\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/13/cong-phuong-quang-hai-chua-ghi-ban-la-chuyen-binh-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y Park cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng vi\u1ec7c ngo\u00e0i chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n: &quot;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00ec c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u00edt tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf V-League 2018. HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft b\u00e0i Quang H\u1ea3i, c\u00f2n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sa s\u00fat do thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Vi\u1ec7c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a ghi b\u00e0n ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. V-League 2018 m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ebd d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/4 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi. C\u1ea3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t cho U23 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-ha-noi-noi-ve-viec-de-quang-hai-ngoi-ngoai-o-vong-4-vleague-168-183341.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/hlv-ha-noi-noi-ve-viec-de-quang-hai-ngoi-ngoai-o-vong-4-vleague.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-ha-noi-noi-ve-viec-de-quang-hai-ngoi-ngoai-o-vong-4-vleague-168-183341.html\">HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Quang H\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 4 V-League</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"748","checkdouble":"183431"},{"date":"10:25 03/04","title":"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f2n \"non\" khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/2/bui-tien-dung-thua-nhan-con-non-khi-len-tuyen-quoc-gia.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor: