acity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf \u0110TQG d\u00f9 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu mon Bui Tien Dung thua nhan con non khi len tuyen quoc gia hinh anh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f2n non khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/3/Thu-mon-Bui-Tien-Dung-thua-nhan-con-non-khi-len-tuyen-quoc-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \"tr\u00ecnh\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110TQG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a NHM. Anh l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 \u1edf hai \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng V-League c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 AFC Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u1edf \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0110TQG gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c anh ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"U23 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia l\u00e0 hai m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u00f4i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00e1c anh V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao\u201d, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh FLC Thanh H\u00f3a cho hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00eda tr\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u00edt ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa t\u00f4i c\u0169ng may m\u1eafn khi b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh, \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u1ecdn \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng FLC Thanh H\u00f3a d\u1ef1 AFC Cup v\u00e0 V.League 2018, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng sinh n\u0103m 1997 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 sai l\u1ea7m. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111i\u1ec1u anh c\u1ea7n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><em>Highlight Thanh H\u00f3a 1-0 SLNA (V\u00f2ng 4 V-League)</em></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-SLNA-vong-4-vleague.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"747","checkdouble":"183432"},{"date":"10:47 03/04","title":"Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng sau v\u00f2ng 4 V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/19/thay-tro-miura-doi-dien-an-phat-nang-sau-vong-4-vleague.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{