\u00e0m b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ea7n Phi S\u01a1n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TP.HCM thang tran thu 2 lien tiep - Anh: Ho Chi Minh Football Club\" title=\"TP.HCM th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp - \u1ea2nh: Ho Chi Minh Football Club\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/tphcm-10-khanh-hoa-phi-son-tiep-tuc-mang-ve-niem-vui-cho-thay-miura.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>CLB TP.HCM c\u1ee7a HLV Miura \u0111ang&nbsp;\u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t do l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n &lsquo;x\u1ea5u x\u00ed&rsquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 6 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V\u0169 Quang Nam, V\u0169 Ng\u1ecdc Th\u1ecbnh, Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Di\u1ec7p, Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Trung, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/trong-tai-tiep-tuc-la-chu-de-gay-tranh-cai-tai-vong-4-vleague-168-183360.html\" target=\"_blank\">l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ea5u x\u00ed c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Miura l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng cho l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. So v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u CLB Ch\u00e2u \u00c1, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, tranh ch\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam mu\u1ed1n l\u00ean t\u1ea7m \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u1edf v\u00f2ng 4 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League 2018</span>, CLB TP.HCM c\u1ee7a HLV Miura&nbsp;c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i l\u0129nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t nh\u1ea5t trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb VFF. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, sau v\u00f2ng 1 V-League 2018, ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n hai tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng do c\u00f3 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<strong><em>Highlight: TPHCM 1-0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a (V\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018)</em></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/tphcm.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#081F2C;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-thua-nhan-con-non-khi-len-tuyen-quoc-gia-168-183432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/2/bui-tien-dung-thua-nhan-con-non-khi-len-tuyen-quoc-gia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-thua-nhan-con-non-khi-len-tuyen-quoc-gia-168-183432.html\">B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f2n non khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf \u0110TQG d\u00f9 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM.</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"746","checkdouble":"183435"},{"date":"09:48 03/04","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u201cgi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u\u201d sao Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/3/psg-mua-trung-ve-alderweireld.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;fl