cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Tottenham (150.000 b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n) song \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u00fd. Ph\u00eda Spurs kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i t\u1eeb l\u00e2u t\u1ea1i CLB. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ebfn sao s\u00e1ng Harry Kane c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 110.000 b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mua trung ve Alderweireld va san sang tra luong cao hinh anh\" title=\"PSG mua trung v\u1ec7 Alderweireld v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/psg-mua-trung-ve-alderweireld.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG mua trung v\u1ec7 Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i PSG mua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-vui-vu-trung-ve-cua-tottenham-172-182837.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>trung v\u1ec7 Alderweireld</strong></span> t\u1edbi sau khi h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Tottenham m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 anh kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/ n\u0103m t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Man United, Chelsea, Real Madrid hay Barcelona \u0111\u1ec1u quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Alderweireld. HLV Mauricio Pochettino t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Daniel Levy \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 gi\u1edd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Tottenham. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Alderweireld v\u1edbi Spurs c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m n\u1eefa m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n g\u00ec v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c kinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a PSG. <br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Toby Alderweireld tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-mua-toby-alderweireld-cung-mu-va-barca-172-183178.html\">V\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn M.U v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-vui-vu-trung-ve-cua-tottenham-172-182837.html\">MU v\u00e0 Chelsea nh\u1eadn tin vui v\u1ee5 trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-mua-toby-alderweireld-voi-mu-172-182539.html\">Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao Tottenham v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-barca-nham-trung-ve-khung-cua-premier-league-180-180959.html\">Barcelona nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-trung-ve-cua-tottenham-nang-cap-hang-thu-180-180233.html\">Real nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Tottenham n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"745","checkdouble":"183423"},{"date":"09:20 03/04","title":"Bayern \u0111em tin vui cho M.U v\u1ee5 James Rodriguez","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/7/26/bayern-dem-tin-vui-cho-mu-vu-james-rodriguez.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-wei