0e8 2018 l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n, ph\u00eda Bayern \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c mua \u0111\u1ee9t ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai James Rodriguez b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bayern Munich theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Anh ra s\u00e2n 28 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, ghi 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng c\u1ea5p 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho muon MU mua James Rodriguez o ky chuyen nhuong He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU mua James Rodriguez \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/10/Mourinho-muon-MU-mua-James-Rodriguez-o-ky-chuyen-nhuong-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai James Rodriguez b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nJames Rodriguez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Bernabeu. Hi\u1ec7n Bayern \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia, \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-voi-james-rodriguez-172-182352.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>MU mua James Rodriguez</strong></span> c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd Bild c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 mua James Rodriguez. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 42 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn NHM v\u00e0 BL\u0110 M.U t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua \u0111\u1ee9t James Rodriguez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/manchester-united-1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>MU </strong></span>mua James Rodriguez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c mua \u0111\u1ee9t ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bayern, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i do Jupp Heynckes x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez so sanh giua Bayern va Real\" title=\"James Rodriguez so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa Bayern v\u00e0 Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/26/bayern-dem-tin-vui-cho-mu-vu-james-rodriguez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua James Rodriguez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00f4ng tin mua \u0111\u1ee9t James Rodriguez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;, Rummenigge ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJames Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-0 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund, anh c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00eam nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/sevilla-vs-bayern-munich-01h45-ngay-0404-sanchez-pizjuan-nuot-tron-hum-xam-184-183405.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Sevilla vs&nbsp;Bayern Munich </strong></span>trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez \u1edf Bundesliga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/107414-41576/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez \u1edf Bundesliga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"744","checkdouble":"183422"},{"date":"08:56 03/04","title":"HLV Allegri c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real: \"Juventus \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/8/hlv-allegri-canh-bao-real-juventus-da-truong-thanh-hon-rat-nhieu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padd