op:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>HLV Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Juventus \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Real \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Juventus v\u00e0 Rea Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf Champions League, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 4-1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Allegri phat bieu ve tran dau Juventus vs Real Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/HLV-Allegri-phat-bieu-ve-tran-dau-Juventus-vs-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Juventus v\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-tu-ket-cup-c1champions-league-201718-18h00-ngay-163-372-182183.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League</strong></span> m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Real g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Juventus. K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng d\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i PSG 5-2 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u00ean ngang ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Juventus, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 Real nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh khi lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 8 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. C\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Juventus c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-vs-real-madrid-01h45-ngay-44-chua-the-tra-thu-184-183419.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Juventus vs Real Madrid</strong></span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc: \u201cTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u00fat ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\u00a01-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Allegri\" title=\"Allegri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/hlv-allegri-canh-bao-real-juventus-da-truong-thanh-hon-rat-nhieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cReal v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn. Real s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu \u0111i. \u0110\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eebng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf La Liga m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u201d, HLV Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tin r\u1eb1ng Real r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i: \u201cH\u1ecd r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/juventus-42.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Juventus</strong></span> ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i Real \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1ea3 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"743","checkdouble":"183421"},{"date":"11:18 03/04","title":"Juventus vs Real Madrid: Ng\u00e0y \u201cb\u00e1u v\u1eadt\u201d tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh Turin","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/3/juventus-vs-real-madrid-ngay-bau-vat-tro-ve-thanh-turin.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Hel