rner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 b\u00e1u v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Turin v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam nay, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Zidane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2016/17 gi\u1edd l\u1ea1i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. 2 trong s\u1ed1 3 m\u00f9a d\u1eabn d\u1eaft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/chiellini-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-than-trong-truoc-real-madrid-184-183417.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid</strong></span>, Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Juventus. Khi c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, Zizou \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juve chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 n\u0103m 1996 t\u1eeb Bordeaux v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean anh r\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Zidane \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o s\u1ecdc \u0111en tr\u1eafng. Gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5y ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, nh\u1eefng pha ch\u1eb7t ch\u00e9m kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0m phong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u0169 c\u00f4ng gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1990, \u0111\u1ea7u 2000, nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Zidane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus vs Real Madrid Ngay bau vat tro ve thanh Turin hinh anh\" title=\"Juventus vs Real Madrid Ng\u00e0y b\u00e1u v\u1eadt tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh Turin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Juventus-vs-Real-Madrid-Ngay-bau-vat-tro-ve-thanh-Turin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zidane khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng nhau, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i. Juventus gi\u00e0nh 6 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf trong khi Zidane c\u0169ng rinh v\u1ec1 1 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng n\u0103m 1998 v\u00e0 2 gi\u1ea3i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a FIFA n\u0103m 1998, 2000. Mark Iuliano &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Zizou t\u1ea1i Juve n\u0103m n\u00e0o t\u1eebng n\u00f3i:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Zidane kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. M\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. M\u1ed7i khi g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn anh \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m, Zidane kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y. Zidane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e1u v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Juventus.</em>&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"44px\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding:10px;\" valign=\"top\"><em>Zidane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e1u v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Juventus</em><br>\r\n            <span style=\"color: #8bc53f; float: right;\"><em>Mark Iuliano</em></span></td>\r\n            <td width=\"44px\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Turin, Zidane ch\u01a1i th\u00e2n v\u1edbi Mauro, con trai \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng Da Angelino, n\u01a1i anh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn d\u00f9ng b\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus. Theo nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh l\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng n\u00e0y k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, anh lu\u00f4n d\u00e0nh ch\u1ed7 cho Zizou v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao Juve khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u00edch: s\u1ed1t c\u00e0 chua, d\u1ea7u oliu, rau h\u00fang qu\u1ebf v\u00e0 pho m\u00e1t Parmesan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi t\u1edbi ch\u01a1i cho Real Madrid n\u0103m 2001 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00ean l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Zidane \u00edt c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp quay l\u1ea1i Turin. Gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League. Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Juventus vs Real Madrid s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ed1n x\u01b0a, th\u0103m l\u1ea1i Mauro v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng Da Angelino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"nha hang Da Angelino\" title=\"nha hang Da Angelino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/nha-hang-Da-Angelino.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng Da Angelino th\u00e2n quen c\u1ee7a Zizou</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Zidane t\u1edbi Turin l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i. S\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0 c\u00f9ng Real gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Juventus \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Zizou \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. 10 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t khi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real, Zidane c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Nacho, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 1 th\u00e1ng do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zidane hop bao\" title=\"HLV Zidane hop bao\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/HLV-Zidane-hop-bao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Zidane trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Juventus vs Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Zidane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Turin bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Nacho v\u00e0 con trai Luca (th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3). 7 th\u00e1ng sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, sau nhi\u1ec1u th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m, Real c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 khi h\u1ea1 Juventus 4-1 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League t\u1ea1i Cardiff n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng th\u1eadt may l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m \u00eam xu\u00f4i. Isco \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong khi Karim Benzema v\u00e0 Gareth Bale c\u0169ng v\u1eady \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB. 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp b\u1ecb Real thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n gi\u00fap h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Las Palmas 3-0 t\u1ea1i La Liga h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMarco Asensio v\u00e0 Lucas Vazquez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng &ldquo;Si\u00eau d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb&rdquo; thay cho Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 James Rodriguez. C\u00f2n Cristiano Ronaldo, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 21/1 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 7-1 c\u1ee7a Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc Deportivo t\u1edbi nay, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 21 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o ch\u1ec9 sau 11 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho CLB, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng ai ngh\u0129 anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 33.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real thang Girona 6-3\" title=\"Real thang Girona 6-3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Real-thang-Girona-6-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong th\u1eddi gian qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i l\u0103n t\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Zidane, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trong th\u1eddi gian qua, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a Los Blancos \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o cho h\u1ecd s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Massimiliano Allegri bi\u1ebft Zizou s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ai cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-vs-real-madrid-01h45-ngay-44-chua-the-tra-thu-184-183419.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid</strong></span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Juventus l\u1ea1i t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Medhi Benatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. Nh\u1eefng Alex Sandro, Federico Bernardeschi v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf 3 tuy\u1ebfn c\u0169ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n Juventus. Th\u00e0nh Turin xem Zidane nh\u01b0 b\u00e1u v\u1eadt, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd h\u1eb3n c\u00f3 ch\u00fat ghen t\u1ecb khi \u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Juventus vs Real Madrid\"