adding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Theo Don Balon, Lionel Messi \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" title=\"Tin chuyen nhuong\" type=\"Tin chuyen nhuong\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018</span></span>.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1eabn l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u sao Sevilla ra s\u00e2n 29 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 26 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi lo so Ivan Rakitic roi Barca o phien cho He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Messi lo s\u1ee3 Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/Messi-lo-so-Ivan-Rakitic-roi-Barca-o-phien-cho-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Rakitic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, song Barca \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Rakitic \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIvan Rakitic \u0111ang lo s\u1ee3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Barca \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m m\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-bang-sao-khung-cua-barca-172-182166.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>MU quan t\u00e2m Rakitic</strong></span>, Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lionel Messi lo s\u1ee3 Rakitic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/messi-khong-muon-barca-ban-rakitic-180-181883.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Lionel Messi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</strong></span> ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou gi\u1eef ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Theo Don Balon, M10 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t s\u1ee3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi khong muon Barca ban cau thu Rakitic\" title=\"Messi kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Barca b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Rakitic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/messi-lo-so-rakitic-se-roi-barca-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi lo s\u1ee3 Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMessi hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t khi Rakitic quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng. Messi \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Barca \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Rakitic v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMessi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Rakitic, anh cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca</strong></span>, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Iniesta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng&nbsp;chia tay s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. N\u1ebfu nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN ra \u0111i, sau \u0111\u00f3 Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Ivan Rakitic \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/7635-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Ivan Rakitic \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"741","checkdouble":"183428"},{"date":"09:08 03/04","title":"Chelsea m\u1ea5t g\u00ec n\u1ebfu sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/chelsea-sa-thai-conte-mat-9-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:4