l-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u201ct\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec5n\u201d Antonio Conte ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edd Daily Telegraph ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, ph\u00eda Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-du-doan-conte-se-bat-bai-khoi-chelsea-172-183389.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Antonio Conte</strong></span>. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea9u tho\u00e1t h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u1eefng Eden Hazard, Thibaut Courtois, Cesc Fabregas, Pedro, Gary Cahill v\u00e0 David Luiz c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Roman Abramovich. HLV Antonio Conte \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 v\u00e0 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n, Champions League v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 4 Premier League v\u1edbi 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m h\u01a1n Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa thai Conte mat 9 trieu bang hinh anh\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte m\u1ea5t 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Chelsea-sa-thai-Conte-mat-9-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Tottenham v\u00e0 k\u00e9m h\u1ecd 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAbramovich v\u00e0 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi thay th\u1ebf Michael Emenalo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh thay m\u1edbi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u1ebfu Chelsea kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a CLB cho hay \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich s\u1ebd \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ra m\u1eb7t x\u1eed l\u00fd n\u1ed9i t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o Chelsea kh\u00f4ng l\u00fan s\u00e2u v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. The Blues v\u1eabn \u0111ang tranh \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00fap FA song g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Europa League l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i phi\u1ec7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Conte\" title=\"HLV Conte\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/HLV-Conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Conte v\u1eabn ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thua-nguoc-spurs-conte-thua-nhan-chelsea-xung-dang-thu-5-172-183351.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</strong></span> l\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1ea3y ra cao h\u01a1n. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 48 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ra \u0111i, nghe \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t ra s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i cho \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Conte, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ee5t d\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng phanh c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, danh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus v\u00e0 \u0110T Italia s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n h\u1ea1i. Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Chelsea t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc song b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Luis Enrique v\u00e0 Thomas Tuchel l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng HLV tr\u1ebb, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerela