th: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino bi soc sau that bai truoc Juventus\" title=\"Pochettino b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/psg-va-real-gap-kho-vu-hlv-tottenham.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pochettino \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" title=\"th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t\" type=\"th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t\">th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span>, song v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/tottenham-hotspur-5.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tottenham </strong></span>\u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Dele Alli hay Harry Kane th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Pochettino l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm HLV c\u1ee7a Tottenham trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Zidane.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Southampton, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Emery. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 Pochettino mua s\u1eafm th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Pochettino</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Tottenham gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Mauricio Pochettino. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino\" title=\"Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/5/Thong-ke-an-tuong-tran-Bournemouth-1-4-Tottenham-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Mauricio Pochettino</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Daily Telegraph, Tottenham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Pochettino, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn 8.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV Southampton kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Tottenham gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/mauricio-pochettino-27.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Mauricio Pochettino</strong></span> l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Tottenham c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea 3-1 ngay t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. V\u1edbi 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Chelsea v\u00e0 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Arsenal, Spurs \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"739","checkdouble":"183426"},{"date":"11:03 03/04","title":"Lacazette n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \"n\u1ed5 s\u00fang\" tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/1/lacazette-noi-gi-sau-khi-no-sung-tro-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family: