 \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Lacazette ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, anh ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ghi ban tro lai, Alexandre Lacazette phat bieu ve Arsenal hinh anh\" title=\"Ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Alexandre Lacazette ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/lacazette-noi-gi-sau-khi-no-sung-tro-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lacazette ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nLacazette t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 11m, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ed5 s\u00fang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal</strong></span>, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Aubameyang kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Europa League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao Lyon hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c, anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon gi\u00fap Lacazette thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lacazette l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n NHM</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/alexandre-lacazette-44374.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Alexandre Lacazette</strong></span> ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, anh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger v\u00e0 NHM: \u201cTh\u1eadt h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian qua th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t\u00a0bu\u1ed3n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lacazette va Aubameyang hoan toan co the choi cung nhau\" title=\"Lacazette v\u00e0 Aubameyang ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/alaca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alexandre Lacazette ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV Wenger, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho t\u00f4i. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n NHM, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n \u1edf b\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng l\u00fac kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. S\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u1eeb C\u0110V lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c tinh th\u1ea7n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n\u201d, Alexandre Lacazette ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, v\u1ec1 HLV Wenger v\u00e0 NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlexandre Lacazette d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Didier Deschamp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi Wissam Ben Yedder c\u1ee7a Sevilla thay th\u1ebf. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf World Cup 2018. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp CSKA Moscow tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 Lacazette ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video Arsenal 3-0 Stoke City (V\u00f2ng 32 Premier League 2017/18)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265133\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/04/01/highlight-arsenal-vs-stoke-vong-32-nha.mp4&autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"738","checkdouble":"183433"},{"date":"14:14 02/04","title":"Say r\u01b0\u1ee3u v\u1eabn l\u00e1i xe, c\u1ef1u sao tr\u1ebb MU b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/say-ruou-van-lai-xe-cuu-sao-tre-mu-bi-doi-bong-cho-ra-duong.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:soli