7a khu v\u1ef1c.<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Biet thu vo chong nha Becks tiep tuc gap rac roi hinh anh\" title=\"Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng nh\u00e0 Becks ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/cc-5335-1522636215.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Becks - Vic \u1edf khu b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean y\u00ean t\u0129nh t\u1ea1i Anh. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho bi\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o g\u1ed3m ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y 6 gian nh\u00e0 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y m\u1edbi v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00ecn ra v\u01b0\u1eddn c\u00e2y \u0103n qu\u1ea3 g\u1ed3m 23 lo\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c nhau. Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tu s\u1eeda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c. R\u1eafc r\u1ed1i li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf v\u00e0 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. \"M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n \u00e0o\", ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb The Sun cho bi\u1ebft.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKhu nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Becks - Vic c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt thu\u1ed9c ho\u00e0ng gia Anh. Theo c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Cotswolds sau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf M\u1ef9.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBecks - Vic b\u00e1n cung \u0111i\u1ec7n Beckingham \u1edf Hertfordshire v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 11,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf Anh, c\u1eb7p v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf ph\u00eda T\u00e2y London. Th\u00e1ng 12/2016, hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng b\u00e1n bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 \u1edf California \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u1edf Cotswolds.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"736","checkdouble":"183381"},{"date":"14:27 02/04","title":"C\u1ef1u sao Arsenal ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa euro","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/cuu-sao-arsenal-phu-nhan-la-ty-phu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"735","checkdouble":"183385"},{"date":"14:34 02/04","title":"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng phim xxx","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/2/cau-thu-bong-da-giai-nghe-de-dong-phim-xxx.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adC