rner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00e2n binh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng 4 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span> v\u1eeba qua, CLB HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00e2n binh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tuy nhi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai m\u1edbi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2 HAGL c\u00f3 th\u00eam hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 H\u1ed3ng Duy, tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 2 b\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00edt sao 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/kho20cho20cong20phuong2c20va20hagl-15226352690101977871689.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u00ea C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 HAGL sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m HAGL kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 x\u01b0a, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, HAGL b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t r\u1ed3i, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i, ch\u1ec9 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u00e1n xem HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i &ldquo;l\u01a1&rdquo; t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Tr\u00ed th\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfp: &ldquo;C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u qu\u00e1. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-thanh-hoa-10-slna-vong-4-vleague-2018-325-183320.html\" target=\"_blank\"> m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n </span>c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i &lsquo;l\u01a1&rsquo; cho r\u1eb1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p SLNA v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng sai l\u1ea7m. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n hay kh\u00f4ng th\u00ec v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u G\u0110KT B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng cho r\u1eb1ng ngo\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, xem kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight HAGL 3-2 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018)</strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/Highlight-HAGL-vs-Nam-Dinh-vong-4-vleague.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\nM\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh-168-183338.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh-168-183338.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-2 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"733","checkdouble":"183387"},{"date":"15:29 02/04","title":"Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ea7u tay c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/nha-cam-quan-nguoi-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-dau-tay-cua-clb-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{fon